<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>관리자 콘솔 - CARON</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f8faff;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Pretendard', sans-serif;
        }
        .login-container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 420px;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .login-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 50px 40px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 43, 92, 0.08);
            text-align: center;
        }
        .login-logo {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .login-logo img {
            height: 45px;
            display: block;
            object-fit: contain;
        }
        .login-header {
            margin-bottom: 35px;
        }
        .login-header h2 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #111;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .login-header p {
            font-size: 15px;
            color: #888;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .form-group label {
            display: block;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #444;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            margin-left: 5px;
        }
        .form-control {
            width: 100%;
            height: 55px;
            padding: 0 20px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            border: 2px solid #eee;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 500;
            outline: none;
            transition: 0.3s;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        .form-control:focus {
            border-color: #002b5c;
            background: #fcfdfe;
        }
        .btn-login {
            width: 100%;
            height: 60px;
            background: #002b5c;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 15px;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 800;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.3s;
            margin-top: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 43, 92, 0.15);
        }
        .btn-login:hover {
            background: #001a35;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0, 43, 92, 0.2);
        }
        .login-footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #aaa;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="login-container">
        <div class="login-card">
            <!-- Logo Section -->
            <div class="login-logo">
                <img src="/images/logo.png" alt="CARON LOGO">
            </div>

            <div class="login-header">
                <h2>ADMIN CONSOLE</h2>
                <p>관리자 계정으로 로그인해 주세요.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Login Form -->
            <form action="/console/login" method="POST">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="username">아이디</label>
                    <input type="text" id="username" name="username" class="form-control" placeholder="아이디를 입력하세요" required>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="password">비밀번호</label>
                    <input type="password" id="password" name="password" class="form-control" placeholder="비밀번호를 입력하세요" required>
                </div>

                <button type="submit" class="btn-login">로그인</button>
            </form>

            <div class="login-footer">
                &copy; 2024 CARON. All rights reserved.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
